A popular American DJ Cipha Sounds has made a startling revelation that popular Nigerian Afrobeat superstar, Wizkid is unknown in America. The DJ stated this at a programme called ROAD podcast involving three other popular DJs. “If it Was Not For Drake Nobody Will Know Wizkid At All, Afrobeats Doesn’t Have Any Star, If you walk down the streets of america now and ask People who Wizkid is, non of them know him,” Cipha Sounds told his colleagues during the podcast. Others on the show were DJSteve1der, Roctakon. Watch the video below: Source